description: Number of planar partitions of n, when partitions that are rotations of each other (when regarded as 3-D objects) are counted only once.
comments: Plane partitions seen as 3-dimensional-objects can have a threefold symmetry axis.
author: _Wouter Meeussen_
extensions: Edited by _N. J. A. Sloane_, Oct 26 2008 at the suggestion of R. J. Mathar.
